  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/gaming/\" rel=\"tag\">游戏产品</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/02/27/tony-hawk-mobile/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://o.aolcdn.com/hss/storage/adam/6c08626e4ae72dbf61343df69dee09dd/tonyhawnphone_630pxhedimg.jpg\" style=\"width: 620px; height: 315px;\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\n久未出现在大家视野中的 Tony Hawk 今天发话了！在接受彭博社专访时这位曾推出过知名游戏「Pro Skater」的滑板大神公布了自己的 2014 年计划。据悉他和他的团队正在打造一款移动平台独占的游戏，而其类型目前还未知，但不出意外应该还是会和滑板运动有关。在暌违游戏届已久后，Hawk 一回来就瞄准了当下最热的移动平台，各位滑板迷们，好好期待一下吧。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2014/02/27/tony-hawk-mobile/\">Engadget</a><br />\n引用来源：<span class=\"source\"><a href=\"http://www.bloomberg.com/video/how-tony-hawk-turned-skateboarding-into-an-empire-ZSxfUQ_XSbmZZqmpgros0g.html\" target=\"_blank\">Bloomberg</a></span><br />\n更多信息：<span class=\"more-coverage\"><a href=\"http://www.joystiq.com/2014/02/27/tony-hawks-new-game-is-exclusively-for-mobiles/\" target=\"_blank\">Joystiq (1)</a></span>、<span class=\"more-coverage\"><a href=\"http://www.joystiq.com/2014/02/20/tony-hawk-and-activision-ride-together-again/\" target=\"_blank\">Joystiq (2)</a></span></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/02/27/tony-hawk-mobile/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20839969/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/02/27/tony-hawk-mobile/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
